    `AssocRICS surveyor with on-the-ground experience of ${townName}'s housing mix and local planning context.`,
    'Reports set out clear priorities, realistic budgets and maintenance tips that support informed negotiations.',
    'Flexible appointments arranged around agents, tenants and busy households.',
    'Aftercare support so you can review findings, compare quotes and plan improvements directly with your surveyor.',
  ],
