      description: 'Concise overview for newer developments or well-maintained homes that need a snapshot of condition.',
    },
    {
      name: 'Independent Damp & Timber Investigation',
      description: 'Identify the cause of damp, mould or timber decay—particularly in sandstone walls and converted outbuildings.',
    },
    {
      name: 'Ventilation & Indoor Air Quality Review',
      description: 'Assess airflow and extractor performance to keep homes comfortable and free from condensation.',
    },
    {
      name: 'Measured Surveys & Planning Support',
      description: 'Precise drawings and feasibility advice for extensions, conversions or planning submissions across Eccleston.',
    },
  ],
};

const localInsights = {
  heading: `What to watch for in ${townName} homes`,
  paragraphs: [
    `Clay soils and mature trees around ${townName} can influence movement and drainage; we inspect cracking, ground levels and soakaways carefully.`,
    `Many homes feature retrofit insulation, replacement windows and upgraded heating. We check detailing and ventilation to avoid trapped moisture or condensation.`,
    `Shared drives, outbuildings and estate-managed boundaries are common. We document responsibilities and maintenance considerations for your solicitor.`,
  ],
};

const additionalInsights = [
  {
    heading: 'Planning, renovation and future works',
    paragraphs: [
      `${townName} households often pursue sympathetic extensions, barn conversions or garden studios. We outline structural considerations, permissions and realistic phasing to keep projects compliant.`,
      'We provide balanced advice on damp treatment, ventilation upgrades and energy improvements so investment delivers comfort without creating new moisture risks.',
    ],
  },
  {
    heading: 'Aftercare and client support',
    paragraphs: [
      'You remain in direct contact with Liam before and after the survey. We review follow-up photos, clarify report items for solicitors and help you prioritise works so decisions are well informed.',
    ],
  },
